query:
SELECT
                id          AS "id!: Uuid",
                comment_id  AS "comment_id!: Uuid",
                user_id     AS "user_id!: Uuid",
                emoji       AS "emoji!",
                created_at  AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
            FROM issue_comment_reactions
            WHERE comment_id IN (SELECT id FROM issue_comments WHERE issue_id = $1)
